tep 1: Set Up Postman
Open Postman.
Create a new collection by clicking on the Collections tab on the left sidebar and then clicking on + New Collection.
Name your collection, for example, "E-commerce API".

Step 2: Add Requests to the Collection
Products Endpoints
    GET /products

    Method: GET
    URL: http://your-api-url/api/products
    Description: Retrieve a list of all products.

    POST /products

    Method: POST
    URL: http://your-api-url/api/products
    Description: Create a new product.
